overview: This is the third of the Superfuckers series, and it gets better with each one. Woodman casts his eye across some of Europe's loveliest backsides as he trolls the streets of Budapest and other cities, looking for hidden beauties. We would love to know what he says to get these girls to do so much. Now there would be one way to make a fortune! Until then, we just have to wait and watch ourselves.
title: Superfuckers 3
